  <text>Foils are used for many purposes, among which <style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:blocks/coil_block" underlined="true">Coils</style>, <style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:circuits/circuit_boards" underlined="true">Circuit Boards</style> and various <style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:circuits/components" underlined="true">Normal</style> and <style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:circuits/smd" underlined="true">SMD</style> components.</text>
  <h3>Crafting</h3>
  <text>Foils can be created manually from a plate using a hammer or using a <style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:machines/bender" underlined="true">Bender</style>, either from ingots directly or from plates.</text>
